<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">临近圣诞节，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总是<delay8 />忍不住去想
准备礼物这事啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我推荐<delay8 />锻炼用品！<delay40 />
能借此把自己锻炼得壮壮实实的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除了礼物还获得了肌肉，超划算！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞节的准备，你都做好了吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想要的<delay8 />礼物清单，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都已经列得明明白白了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不眠不休地<delay8 />写了100样，<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />应该能至少得到一件<delay20 />
想要的东西吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">看着广场上的树，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就感觉<delay8 />特别有圣诞节的气氛，<delay20 />
真是叫人坐立不安啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能让自己冷静下来，<delay8 />
最近我每天<delay8 />都在岛上奔跑，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且第二天还能感受到肌肉酸痛，<delay8 />感觉超棒！</message>
</msbt>